comment: Global offset is -1.5 to compensate glass-supported homing procedure. 500 + 500 (layer 5) µL T3. Pause after layer 4. 21/21 complete after printing with minor surface defects. Dipping of printhead in DPBS for washing. Minor damage to bottom sides during collection from printhead with spatula. Post-curing 30 min in FormCure at RT in petri dish with DPBS. Packing in 2 ml Eppi with DPBS.
